<nav class='breadcrumb m4 show-lg'>Participate&nbsp;&nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;</nav>

<h1 class='h1 h1--alt m2'>
Organize a local TEDx event
</h1>
<!-- PB:B: image --><div class='pages-image'>
<img alt='TEDx-ers ' class='pages-image__content' src='//pb-assets.tedcdn.com/system/baubles/files/000/001/235/original/TEDx-Organize-hero_859x300px.jpg?1404130239'>
</div>


<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='p2'>
<p>Think of TEDx as hosting an awesome dinner party, with great food, inspirational videos, brilliant speakers and mind-blowing conversation. By organizing a TEDx event, you will have the opportunity to create a truly unique event that will unleash new ideas, inspire and inform.</p>

</div>


</div>

<div class='row'>
<div class='col-lg-6'>
<!-- PB:B: heading --><h3 class="h4 m4" id="h2--a-new-organizer">A new organizer?
</h3>

<!-- PB:B: heading --><h4 class="h7 m5" id="h3--before-you-start">Before you start
</h4>

<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='copy text-left'>
<p><a href="/participate/organize-a-local-tedx-event/before-you-start/the-tedx-experience/what-is-a-tedx-event">What is a TEDx event?</a> What a TEDx event is and isn't.<br>
<a href="/participate/organize-a-local-tedx-event/before-you-start/the-tedx-experience/your-responsibilities">Your responsibilities</a> TEDx takes time, and effort.<br>
<a href="/participate/organize-a-local-tedx-event/before-you-start/the-basics">The basics</a> What you need when applying for an event. </p>

</div>



<!-- PB:B: heading --><h4 class="h7 m5" id="h3--ready">Ready?
</h4>

<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='copy text-left'>
<p><a href="/participate/organize-a-local-tedx-event/before-you-start/tedx-rules">Read the rules</a><br>
<a href="/participate/organize-a-local-tedx-event/before-you-start/the-basics/naming-your-event">Pick a name for your event</a><br>
<a href="/tedx/licenses">Apply for a TEDx license</a></p>

</div>



<!-- PB:B: horizontal_rule --><hr class='pages-hr'>


